        "end_time": 28.987291666666664,
        "duration": 18.685333333333332,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_003.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "You know what we haven't talked about in a while?",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 1.82
            },
            {
                "text": "Things that matter.",
                "start": 1.96,
                "end": 3.28
            },
            {
                "text": "Like mass and materials and particles.",
                "start": 3.28,
                "end": 5.38
            },
            {
                "text": "I guess what I mean is things that have to do with matter.",
                "start": 5.54,
                "end": 9.02
            },
            {
                "text": "We've already talked a lot",
                "start": 9.02,
                "end": 10.46
            },
            {
                "text": "about the different states of matter.",
                "start": 10.46,
                "end": 11.94
            },
            {
                "text": "You know, some matter comes in the form of a solid,",
                "start": 11.94,
                "end": 14.36
            },
            {
                "text": "others in a liquid, and still others in a gas.",
                "start": 14.4,
                "end": 16.94
            },
            {
                "text": "But are you ready for",
                "start": 16.94,
                "end": 18.66
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at a desk and speaks."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 14.04,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "SOLID"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 15.24,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "LIQUID"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 16.44,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "GAS"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 4,
        "start_frame": 696,
        "end_frame": 842,
        "start_time": 29.028999999999996,
        "end_time": 35.11841666666666,
        "duration": 6.089416666666665,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_004.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "or a question that will bend your brain a little.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 2.12
            },
            {
                "text": "What if there's matter that fits into more",
                "start": 2.12,
                "end": 4.3
            },
            {
                "text": "than one of these categories?",
                "start": 4.3,
                "end": 5.68
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at her desk and gestures with her hands."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 2.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "BIG QUESTION\nWHAT IF THERE'S MATTER THAT FITS INTO MORE THAN ONE OF THESE CATEGORIES?"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 5,
        "start_frame": 843,
        "end_frame": 1002,
        "start_time": 35.160125,
        "end_time": 41.79175,
        "duration": 6.631625,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_005.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Is there such a thing?",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 0.8
            },
            {
                "text": "If there is, what's it like?",
                "start": 0.8,
                "end": 2.6
            },
            {
                "text": "And can I make some?",
                "start": 2.6,
                "end": 3.68
            },
            {
                "text": "Maybe in my kitchen.",
                "start": 3.82,
                "end": 5.78
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "BIG QUESTION\nIS THERE SUCH A THING?"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 1.07,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "BIG QUESTION\nIF THERE IS, WHAT'S IT LIKE?"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 2.13,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "BIG QUESTION\nAND CAN I MAKE SOME?\nMAYBE IN MY KITCHEN."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 3.07,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at her desk."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 6,
        "start_frame": 1003,
        "end_frame": 1188,
        "start_time": 41.83345833333333,
        "end_time": 49.549499999999995,
        "duration": 7.716041666666662,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_006.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Before I answer any of these questions, let's take a closer look at different states of matter.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 7.62
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "BIG QUESTION"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 4.03,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at her desk and gestures with her hands as she speaks."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 7,
        "start_frame": 1189,
        "end_frame": 1447,
        "start_time": 49.59120833333333,
        "end_time": 60.35195833333333,
        "duration": 10.760750000000002,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_007.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "You remember what a solid is.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 1.22
            },
            {
                "text": "It's matter that has a definite size and shape.",
                "start": 1.22,
                "end": 3.48
            },
            {
                "text": "Like this desk that I'm sitting at,",
                "start": 3.48,
                "end": 5.06
            },
            {
                "text": "or the clothes that I'm wearing,",
                "start": 5.06,
                "end": 6.3
            },
            {
                "text": "and well, all of me.",
                "start": 6.3,
                "end": 8.08
            },
            {
                "text": "I'm a person with a definite size and shape.",
                "start": 8.08,
                "end": 10.62
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "SOLID\nMATTER THAT HAS\nA DEFINITE SIZE\nAND SHAPE"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at her desk and gestures with her hands as she speaks."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 8,
        "start_frame": 1448,
        "end_frame": 1631,
        "start_time": 60.39366666666666,
        "end_time": 68.02629166666667,
        "duration": 7.632625000000004,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_008.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Liquid is matter that has a definite size,",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 1.7
            },
            {
                "text": "but no definite shape.",
                "start": 1.7,
                "end": 3.1
            },
            {
                "text": "The water in this glass is a liquid.",
                "start": 3.1,
                "end": 4.98
            },
            {
                "text": "It has a definite size, but no definite shape.",
                "start": 4.98,
                "end": 7.5
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "LIQUID\nMATTER THAT HAS A\nDEFINITE SIZE BUT\nNO DEFINITE SHAPE"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Water pours into glass against black background."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 9,
        "start_frame": 1632,
        "end_frame": 1760,
        "start_time": 68.068,
        "end_time": 73.40666666666667,
        "duration": 5.3386666666666684,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_009.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Like, you could say that my desk is desk shaped, but there's no such thing as water shaped.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 4.96
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at a desk and gestures with her hands as she speaks."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 3.5,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina spins a globe on the desk."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 10,
        "start_frame": 1761,
        "end_frame": 1846,
        "start_time": 73.448375,
        "end_time": 76.99358333333333,
        "duration": 3.545208333333335,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_010.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "And gas is matter that has no definite size or shape.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 3.1
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "GAS\nMATTER THAT HAS\nNO DEFINITE SIZE\nOR SHAPE"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina continues to sit at her desk, gesturing as she speaks."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 11,
        "start_frame": 1847,
        "end_frame": 2142,
        "start_time": 77.03529166666667,
        "end_time": 89.33924999999999,
        "duration": 12.303958333333327,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_011.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "The air around me and you is a gas.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 1.84
            },
            {
                "text": "It's not shaped like anything and its size changes depending on how big the container",
                "start": 1.98,
                "end": 6.5
            },
            {
                "text": "is that it's in.",
                "start": 6.5,
                "end": 7.4
            },
            {
                "text": "Now, all solids, liquids, and gases are materials or objects made of matter.",
                "start": 7.4,
                "end": 12.2
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at her desk, gesturing as she speaks. Animated clouds float around her."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 8.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "MATERIAL: AN OBJECT MADE OF MATTER."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 8.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "The animated clouds disappear. Sabrina gestures towards a small globe on her desk."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 12,
        "start_frame": 2143,
        "end_frame": 2580,
        "start_time": 89.38095833333333,
        "end_time": 107.60749999999999,
        "duration": 18.226541666666662,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_012.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "And all materials have properties, or traits that help identify them, like their color, or shape, or size, or temperature, or weight.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 6.84
            },
            {
                "text": "And now that you're properly refreshed on the states of matter, I'm going to cheat and answer our big question a little early.",
                "start": 6.84,
                "end": 12.56
            },
            {
                "text": "Or at least part of it.",
                "start": 12.56,
                "end": 14.42
            },
            {
                "text": "Yes, some materials aren't so easily lumped into just one state of matter.",
                "start": 14.42,
                "end": 18.06
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "PROPERTY: A DISTINGUISHING QUALITY OF AN OBJECT MADE OF MATTER, LIKE ITS COLOR, SHAPE, SIZE, TEMPERATURE, OR WEIGHT"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at her desk, gesturing as she speaks. A globe sits on the desk beside her."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 4.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "COLOR\nSHAPE\nSIZE\nTEMPERATURE\nWEIGHT"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 8.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina clasps her hands together."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 13.8,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina spreads her hands."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 13,
        "start_frame": 2581,
        "end_frame": 2672,
        "start_time": 107.64920833333332,
        "end_time": 111.44466666666666,
        "duration": 3.795458333333343,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_013.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "These unusual materials can actually act like multiple states of matter.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 3.42
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "THESE UNUSUAL MATERIALS CAN ACTUALLY ACT LIKE MULTIPLE STATES OF MATTER."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at her desk, gesturing as she speaks. A globe sits on the desk beside her."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 14,
        "start_frame": 2673,
        "end_frame": 2845,
        "start_time": 111.486375,
        "end_time": 118.66020833333333,
        "duration": 7.173833333333334,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_014.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Neat, right?",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 0.52
            },
            {
                "text": "Wanna meet just such a material?",
                "start": 0.52,
                "end": 1.92
            },
            {
                "text": "Then let me introduce you to non-Newtonian fluids.",
                "start": 1.92,
                "end": 5.18
            },
            {
                "text": "The non-what now?",
                "start": 5.78,
                "end": 6.78
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina continues gesturing as she speaks."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 4.17,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "NON-NEWTONIAN FLUIDS"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 15,
        "start_frame": 2846,
        "end_frame": 3182,
        "start_time": 118.70191666666666,
        "end_time": 132.71591666666666,
        "duration": 14.013999999999996,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_015.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Non-Newtonian fluids are substances",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 1.34
            },
            {
                "text": "that don't behave like we expect them to.",
                "start": 1.34,
                "end": 3.68
            },
            {
                "text": "These fluids might look like one thing,",
                "start": 3.68,
                "end": 6.06
            },
            {
                "text": "but they behave like another.",
                "start": 6.06,
                "end": 7.76
            },
            {
                "text": "So, what makes a substance non-Newtonian?",
                "start": 7.76,
                "end": 10.48
            },
            {
                "text": "Let's find out by making a non-Newtonian mixture of our own.",
                "start": 10.48,
                "end": 13.68
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina continues talking and gesturing with her hands."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 10.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "INVESTIGATION\nLET\u2019S FIND OUT BY MAKING A NON-NEWTONIAN MIXTURE OF OUR OWN."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
