            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "A teal measuring cup, clear bowl, yellow container of cornstarch, and a teal spoon appear on a white surface against a green backdrop."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 2.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "1 1/2 C. CORNSTARCH + 1 C. WATER"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 3.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "1 1/2 C. CORNSTARCH + 1 C. WATER + BIG BOWL"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 4.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "1 1/2 C. CORNSTARCH + 1 C. WATER + BIG BOWL + SPOON"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 22,
        "start_frame": 4097,
        "end_frame": 4175,
        "start_time": 170.87904166666667,
        "end_time": 174.13229166666665,
        "duration": 3.25324999999998,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_022.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Pour the cornstarch into your bowl and slowly add some water.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 2.88
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina adds cornstarch to a bowl and slowly adds water."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 23,
        "start_frame": 4176,
        "end_frame": 4614,
        "start_time": 174.17399999999998,
        "end_time": 192.44224999999997,
        "duration": 18.268249999999995,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_023.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Keep stirring until the mixture feels kind of like honey.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 2.16
            },
            {
                "text": "In the end, it should look like this.",
                "start": 2.16,
                "end": 4.2
            },
            {
                "text": "Now grab some of this goo in your hand.",
                "start": 4.36,
                "end": 6.4
            },
            {
                "text": "When you squeeze it, it'll form a solid ball in your palm.",
                "start": 6.4,
                "end": 9.32
            },
            {
                "text": "But when you unclench your fist and release the pressure, it'll slide between your fingers,",
                "start": 9.94,
                "end": 14.36
            },
            {
                "text": "like a liquid.",
                "start": 14.64,
                "end": 15.84
            },
            {
                "text": "All fluids have a property known as viscose.",
                "start": 15.84,
                "end": 18.18
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina stirs the mixture in a bowl."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 6.83,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina picks up the mixture."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 7.66,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina squeezes the mixture, forming a ball."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 8.11,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "SOLID"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 13.33,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina opens her hand, and the mixture flows."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 14.77,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "LIQUID"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 24,
        "start_frame": 4615,
        "end_frame": 4692,
        "start_time": 192.48395833333333,
        "end_time": 195.69549999999998,
        "duration": 3.2115416666666476,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_024.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "which is basically the rate at which a fluid flows.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 2.58
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "DEFINITION\nVISCOSITY\nTHE RATE AT WHICH A\nFLUID FLOWS."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Animated definition of viscosity appears on screen."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 25,
        "start_frame": 4693,
        "end_frame": 4860,
        "start_time": 195.7372083333333,
        "end_time": 202.7025,
        "duration": 6.965291666666673,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_025.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Newtonian fluids, or normal fluids, flow at a consistent rate, but non-Newtonian fluids, or non-normal fluids,",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 6.88
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at a desk and speaks to the camera."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 4.5,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina places her hands together on the desk."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 26,
        "start_frame": 4861,
        "end_frame": 4978,
        "start_time": 202.74420833333332,
        "end_time": 207.62408333333332,
        "duration": 4.879874999999998,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_026.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "flow at a different rate depending on how much force",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 3.04
            },
            {
                "text": "or pressure is applied to them.",
                "start": 3.04,
                "end": 4.46
            },
            {
                "text": "So",
                "start": 4.46,
                "end": 4.7
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "FLOW AT A DIFFERENT RATE, DEPENDING ON HOW MUCH FORCE OR PRESSURE IS APPLIED TO THEM."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at a desk and speaks to the camera."
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "scene_number": 27,
        "start_frame": 4979,
        "end_frame": 5387,
        "start_time": 207.66579166666665,
        "end_time": 224.68279166666665,
        "duration": 17.016999999999996,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_027.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "So your oobleck flows at a much slower rate when pressure is applied to it, acting like a solid.",
                "start": 0.0,
                "end": 4.56
            },
            {
                "text": "But when the pressure is removed, it flows faster and behaves like a liquid.",
                "start": 4.56,
                "end": 8.74
            },
            {
                "text": "Good for you, oobleck! Being normal is overrated, right?",
                "start": 8.74,
                "end": 12.04
            },
            {
                "text": "So...",
                "start": 16.21,
                "end": 16.99
            }
        ],
        "captions": [],
        "audio_clips": [
            {
                "start_time": 0.0,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Sabrina sits at a desk and speaks to the camera."
            },
            {
                "start_time": 4.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "SOLID"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 8.0,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "LIQUID"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 12.57,
                "type": "Text on Screen",
                "text": "CONCLUSION"
            },
            {
                "start_time": 12.57,
                "type": "Visual",
                "text": "Animated Sabrina floats in space with a parachute."
