        "end_frame": 5808,
        "start_time": 232.23199999999997,
        "end_time": 242.242,
        "duration": 10.01000000000002,
        "scene_path": "videos/Fnd-2jetT1w/Fnd-2jetT1w_scenes/scene_030.mp4",
        "transcript": [
            {
                "text": "Which means, yes, some materials can fit into more than just one state of matter.",
